Package com.dougnoel.sentinel.elements

Contains all of the classes for creating web elements and acting upon them.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Button
    Button implementation of a PageElement.
    Checkbox
    Check box implementation of a PageElement.
    Div
    Div implementation of a WebElement.
    Dropdown
    Dropdown implementation of a WebElement.
    ElementFunctions
    Retrieves as an element as a PageElement or as one of the following types: - Button, Checkbox, Div, Dropdown, GoogleMap, Link, Radio, Select, Span, Table, Textbox To return as the desired type, we call getElement which returns a PageElement, and the element is then typecast as the desired element.
    GoogleMap
    Google Maps implementation of a Div WebElement.
    IFrame
    IFrame implementation of a WebElement.
    Label
    Div implementation of a WebElement.
    Link
    Hyperlink (Link) implementation of a WebElement.
    PageElement
    Base element class that handles creation of element types and allows late binding.
    PageSelectElement
    Extends PageElement.
    Radiobutton
    Radio button implementation of a PageSelectElement.
    Span
    Span implementation of a WebElement.
    Table
    Implements a Table WebElement.
    Textbox
    Textbox implementation of a PageElement.

Package com.dougnoel.sentinel.elements Description
